# Working on the floor: laptop on lap, screen dim. 7 rows (vs the
# static seated_floor's 6) — adds a keyboard row beneath the screen
# bezel so the laptop reads as a clamshell, not just a slab.
@frame 0
. n H H H H n .
n H H H H H H n
H S e S S e S H
. S S S m S S .
. B B B B B B .
K j j j j j j K
. k k k k k k .
